E-05 ENTERED PART NO. NOT FOUND IN FIXED ORDER-PLACEMENT FILE.
E-06 NOT FOUND IN A-PICS2 PLAN PUBLICATION CONTROL M/F.
E-07 ALREADY CANCELED.
E-08 DATA DOES NOT EXIST.
